      "title": "context preview",
      "properties": {
        "cnr_id": "comfyui-custom-scripts",
        "ver": "609f3afaa74b2f88ef9ce8d939626065e3247469",
        "Node name for S&R": "ShowText|pysssss",
        "ue_properties": {
          "widget_ue_connectable": {},
          "input_ue_unconnectable": {},
          "version": "7.5.1"
        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Context 1\n\n# Style schemas (reference block)\n\nUse these as reusable \"style blocks\" you can paste into prompts or keep in `extra_context`.\n\n## Photoreal\n- Medium: photography, photoreal, natural texture\n- Lighting: realistic, soft key + fill, believable shadows\n- Camera: 35mm/50mm, shallow depth of field (optional)\n- Constraints: no plastic skin, no CGI look\n\n## Cinematic\n- Mood: cinematic, dramatic contrast, filmic color grade\n- Lighting: rim light, volumetric haze (optional)\n- Camera: anamorphic, wide establishing / tight close-up (specify)\n- Details: bokeh, film grain (subtle)\n\n## Anime / Illustration\n- Medium: anime illustration, clean linework\n- Shading: cel shading / soft shading (pick one)\n- Color: vibrant palette, controlled highlights\n- Constraints: consistent character design, clean anatomy\n\n## Comic / Graphic Novel\n- Medium: inked comic, bold outlines\n- Shading: crosshatch / halftone (pick one)\n- Color: limited palette (optional)\n- Composition: dynamic angles, strong silhouettes\n\n## 3D / CGI\n- Medium: 3D render, PBR materials\n- Lighting: studio softbox / HDRI (specify)\n- Camera: realistic lens + DOF (optional)\n- Constraints: avoid uncanny skin, avoid low-poly artifacts\n\n## Pixel Art\n- Medium: pixel art, limited palette\n- Resolution: specify (e.g. 64×64, 128×128)\n- Constraints: crisp pixels, no anti-aliasing, no gradients unless dithered\n\n## Watercolor\n- Medium: watercolor painting on textured paper\n- Edges: soft bleeding, granulation\n- Color: transparent washes, subtle blooms\n\n## Oil Painting\n- Medium: oil on canvas, visible brushstrokes\n- Lighting: painterly highlights, rich shadows\n- Color: warm/cool balance, layered paint\n\n## Minimal / Flat\n- Medium: flat vector, minimal shapes\n- Color: 2–5 colors, clean spacing\n- Constraints: no textures, no gradients (unless requested)\n\n## UI / Product Mock\n- Medium: UI screenshot / product render (specify)\n- Layout: grid, spacing system, typography scale\n- Constraints: readable text, consistent alignment\n\n---\n\n## Add a new style (copy/paste template)\n### <STYLE NAME>\n- Medium:\n- Lighting:\n- Color:\n- Composition:\n- Camera (optional):\n- Constraints:\n\n\n## Context 2\n\n# Z-Image prompting quick schema\n\nGeneral:\n- Plain language, describe what should be in-frame.\n- Specify style/medium and lighting.\n- If you want a specific layout, describe the composition.\n\nTemplate:\nSubject: ...\nBackground: ...\nStyle: ...\nLighting: ...\nComposition: ...\nDetails: ..."
      ]
