      "widgets_values": [
        "Subject: A dark, industrial metal walkway or catwalk stretching into a foggy, overcast distance, viewed from a low, straight-on perspective. The floor is a heavy, grated metal grid.\nBackground: A gloomy, grey, foggy sky visible at the end of the walkway.\nStyle: Cinematic, gritty, high-contrast, filmic color grade.\nLighting: Dim, moody, atmospheric, with a soft, diffused key light from the foggy horizon and subtle rim lighting on the metal structures.\nComposition: Central one-point perspective, symmetrical, leading lines drawing the eye to the vanishing point.\nDetails: Add a large, bright lime-green \"X\" logo in the top-left corner. Add the text \"CY.CEPNETILS\" in a bold, distressed, white stencil font across the bottom third. Add small, scattered lime-green geometric markers (triangles, lines) around the frame edges.\nMedium: Photorealistic photography with a heavy digital overlay and posterization effect.\nConstraints: High contrast, deep blacks, grainy texture, slightly desaturated colors except for the neon green accents."
      ]
